					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">From what I can see from hqx on google code, it doesn't use the alpha channel when calculating RGB values so it won't look correct. That implementation is optimized for solid colours and simply does not work with transparency. I'm not sure if the one you used does the same, but if so than we need to find one that works or test it with another algorithm. Thank you for those images!</div>

